{"tid":591944,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"網台赤裸話題應有盡有 杜汶澤自爆性能力","createTime":"2018-03-14T01:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T05:06:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"109416a6165d752dd3db40739c709e8fd4a8b42e","tid":591944,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:11:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180314/20330774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F20330774&d=W%2BH%2FhQi2htBT%2FNrt%2BuYF%2FJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=bcab87eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F20330774&h=5cb21e10\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180314/20330774</a><br />\n<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】網台赤裸話題應有盡有<br />\n杜汶澤自爆性能力<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人   <br />\n         <br />\n食腦杜汶澤睇好數碼化時代嘅大趨勢，籌備咗幾個月嘅網台，將喺下周五（23號）開台，當晚10點喺facebook開live，佢仲溫馨提示呼籲要睇《杜汶澤喱騷》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180314/large/14ec5p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180314%2Flarge%2F14ec5p2.jpg&h=6ff791e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜汶澤同新女貝依霖學腳底按摩時，轉話題話要教師傅空手道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180314/large/14ec5p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180314%2Flarge%2F14ec5p4.jpg&h=a9989867&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n約性治療師何慕詩見面嘅杜汶澤，喺鏡頭前大爆自慰次數。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180314/large/14ec5p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180314%2Flarge%2F14ec5p1.jpg&h=e1789603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為加入杜汶澤嘅網台，有女生面試時大跳鋼管舞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教服侍老公<br />\n<br />\n講到網台，阿澤噚日喺電話訪問中話：「我幫ViuTV同奇妙電視拍好多節目，發覺有啲idea好想自己搞，電視台尺度、級別唔可以太大膽，我自己畀錢拍。」阿澤仲構思緊好多真人騷，佢話：「有啲係教育節目，搵江若琳教識佢點樣做個好老婆，教佢點服侍好老公，咁就永遠唔出去滾，永遠唔變心。」阿澤話佢嘅節目好多元化：「又啱家庭觀眾，又啱主婦睇，你唔睇就笨。」<br />\n<br />\n《杜汶澤喱騷》預告片強調會迎合唔同智商同道德層嘅觀眾，阿澤喺片中同旗下新女貝依霖去學腳底按摩，佢仲同師傅交流手勢用力，將話題扯到要教番師傅空手道，更搞笑示範：「等手掌放鬆就啪落去（下體），啪完佢直接去歌連臣角。」阿澤又同性治療師何慕詩面談，喺鏡頭前大爆自慰次數，坦誠向性治療師形容自己狀態，娛樂「性」豐富。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180314/large/14ec5p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180314%2Flarge%2F14ec5p3.jpg&h=a35d917e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜汶澤（左二）去日本拍節目，仲去牛郎店執過形象。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不惜出股惑<br />\n<br />\n早前同盤菜瑩子去日本拍《日本風涼話》，阿澤話去得日本唔少得去購物，去到性商店見到貨架擺滿潤滑劑，阿澤目不轉睛，盤菜瑩子就笑言有WD-40，阿澤聽後笑爆，忍唔住寸咗盤菜瑩子：「度門生銹呀，老公買支WD-40返嚟。」預告片中仲有剪咗面試時花絮，有一個女生大玩鋼管舞，為份工不惜出「股惑」，令阿澤看到眼瞪瞪。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：馮仁昭"},{"pid":"7fcb1e5c956c52fe64ccd0bc73ee9e2d5b4c81cc","tid":591944,"uid":71237,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:12:59.000Z","msg":"無人想知佢嘅性能力"},{"pid":"7c801a82e7a8e194265b0694db458eace520e96a","tid":591944,"uid":144843,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:13:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9fe521f9d4d69055f3eb7a8664d4f669edd6516b","tid":591944,"uid":169892,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:15:02.000Z","msg":"對佢冇好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed7f758452b08055556232954462d8c8b109acf","tid":591944,"uid":139671,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:16:00.000Z","msg":"大膽敢言好藝人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa118b74097ffa282892df88048c7846e57c36b","tid":591944,"uid":119959,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0